---
title: Mumbai Chicken & Spiced Roast Veggies with Lemon Yoghurt & Slivered Almonds
description: This gorgeous plate of colour doesn't just look good - it's a nutritionally balanced combo of lemon yoghurt,
succulent chicken, rainbow roasted veggies and crunchy almonds. Flavour is just written all over it.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
